<div class='panel'><h3>What is the goal of this instance ?</h3>

<p>This instance if open to everyone. We are talking about programming, video games, electronics, computer, music, mangas, animes, high-tech and a lot of other things...</p>

<p>tootodon.xyz don't take use of advertising or external analytics software and does not make any money with your informations.</p>
<p>Instead you can help us by dropping a small donation.</p>

<p>Follow <a href="https://tootodon.xyz/@announcement">@announcement</a> for status updates, planned downtimes, etc.</p>

<h3>Who's behind tootodon.xyz ?</h3>

<p>Only one admin currently manage this Mastodon instance. If you want to help and join the team please contact <a href="https://tootodon.xyz/@nnjeremy">@nnjeremy</a>.</p>

<p>The team :</p>
<div class='features-list'>
<div class='features-list__column'>
<ul class='fa-ul'>
    <li><i class="fa fa-li fa-user-circle"></i><a href="https://tootodon.xyz/@nnjeremy">@nnjeremy</a>, <a href="https://tootodon.xyz/@nnjeremy/22931">Introduction</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

<p>We're just volunteers, so problems can occur on this server. We are not responsible if data are lost or if service is interrupted. You've been warned..</p>

<h3>What are the rules ?</h3>

<div class='features-list'>
<div class='features-list__column'>
<ul class='fa-ul'>
    <li><i class="fa fa-li fa-check-circle"></i>Since the server is hosted in France, you must respect the Law of France.</li>
    <li><i class="fa fa-li fa-check-circle"></i>Allowed languages: English, French (more language available as sone as we find more moderator)</li>
    <li><i class="fa fa-li fa-check-circle"></i>Racism, xenophobia, homophobia are strictly prohibited.</li>
    <li><i class="fa fa-li fa-check-circle"></i>Lolicon, immoral and indecent child pics are strictly prohibited</li>
    <li><i class="fa fa-li fa-check-circle"></i>NSFW is allowed only in Content Warning.</li>
    <li><i class="fa fa-li fa-check-circle"></i>Gory, bloody and violent pictures only in Content Warning.</li>
    <li><i class="fa fa-li fa-check-circle"></i>Don't be a troll, Don't be a bully.</li>
    <li><i class="fa fa-li fa-check-circle"></i>Don't be a jerk, please.</li>
    <li><i class="fa fa-li fa-check-circle"></i>You can report every post you judge offensive.</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

<p>Any user not respecting these rules may get silenced or suspended.<br/>
<p>Bot accounts can be silenced if there are too much complains about them.</p>

